<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个胶体是你的泡泡糖？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”玛拉喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吹了一个泡泡，它变得越来越大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个胶体又发出了轰隆声。咕噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西抓起玛拉，想带她飞到一个安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们停在一个高楼的楼顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，火箭女孩儿！”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和玛拉看到胶体变得越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咕噜！胶体很快就覆盖了整个城市的街区！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你嚼的是什么泡泡糖？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉从口袋里掏出那盒泡泡糖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个新产品。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它叫‘威格尔斯夫人口香糖’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“威格尔斯夫人？”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在美罗城近郊有一家新的糖果工厂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许我应该去跟......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟谁？”在她们身后传来一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转过身，看到一个高个子女人站在那里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>带着一顶高高的帽子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是威格尔斯夫人。”那个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快我的泡泡糖胶体会覆盖整个城市！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除非布洛姆市长给我一百万美元，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>否则胶体会一直留在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西怒视着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只是你的想法，威格尔斯夫人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向坏人靠近了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西听到了叫喊声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我们，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西往下看去，发现有几个人困在胶体里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一会儿见，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从外套里掏出一条长长的绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把绳子抛向楼底，然后顺着绳子滑下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆长得像果冻豆的卡车在楼下等着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人跳上车开走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看向玛拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这儿等着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西迅速飞向胶体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抓住一个男人的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请救救我，火箭女孩儿！”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想被泡泡糖吃掉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别紧张。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会带你离开这里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把大家从胶体里拉了出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并带着所有的人飞到安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胶体不断延伸着，黏住了更多的大楼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就覆盖了整个美罗城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真受不了这个可恶的胶体。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！她的眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轰隆！泡泡糖胶体被炸成了上百个碎片！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“太好了。再也没有......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咕噜！咕噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，地面开始晃动，到处都是轰隆声，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的小胶体都在动，都在变大！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来我把事情变得更糟了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>